metadata.name: System Œ± #34
metadata.description:
"To capture the fleeting time in the generating process."

In this work,I d'like focus on the generating of generative art system itself rather than imitate some scene or style.
And with the flow of time, try to figure out where it can take me toward.

This work would be a series of my alternative view on generative art.
"Œ±" means the first step of this series.

Press [s] in live view to save file as PNG.
Press [p] to stop.

------
Happy first birthday fx(hash) !!

20% of primary revenues go to Savepakistan Flood Relief Fundraiser.
20% of primary revenues go to the Processing foundation.

metadata.name: [fxhashturnsone] 2022 A Generative Odyssey #341
metadata.description:
ü™êüåå‚ú®

2022 A Generative Odyssey (Story of a traveler)

A simple space landscape generator üèû
Allows some exploration for curious ones üì°
Don't forget to press "4" to take a panoramic picture üì∏ü§≥

üï≥üß≠üõ∞



-----
* Technics *

- JavaScript / ThreeJS / WebGL
- Pure code / no external assets
- Interactive / orbitable
- 8 scenes with unlimited possible variations
- 5 capture / screenshot modes 8K+

-----
* Controls *

Left click / touch + drag : orbit around center of interest
Wheel/pinch : zoom in/out
Keyboard "R" : enable automatic rotation of view

Keyboard "1" : PNG capture the current view at same resolution / ratio 
Keyboard "2" : PNG capture view as square 4320x4320
Keyboard "3" : PNG capture at best resolution 8K (7680x4320)
Keyboard "4" : PNG capture as panoramic view (8192x2304)
Keyboard "5" : PNG capture as super-panoramic (10650x3000)

-----
* URL modifier *

"&r=1"
enables auto rotation of view (equivalent to "R" key press)

-----
* Mint details *

- Mint preview / capture is PNG 1920x1920

-----
@HAL09999 ‚Äì May/November 2022

Rotate and zoom with the mouse to explore the model

metadata.name: Play with lines #3 #35
metadata.description:
Life starts from a point
Dots become lines in union
And the lines make our world


Play with lines
This collection is the result of my play with the lines I drew with the tablet in an unbalanced state of mind.
And combining these lines with digital paintings in the background
This collection has 5 layers
The first layer contains oil paintings as a background
The second layer of hatches
The third layer of the lines I have drawn with the tablet is 25 different images
The fourth layer of different covers
The fifth layer of the box and signature

metadata.name: NeoPrimal #245
metadata.description:
A story of (un)civilized Homosapiens trapped in a metropolitan nightmare, hoping to feel alive among all of the chaos..
------------------
Live-view_
Resolution: Add "&res=" end of your url with a resolution multiplier. (1-2-4) (Default:2=2400x3200px)
Press S: Saves the current scene.
LeftMouse: Controls the zoom level.
------------------
Created with p5.js

metadata.description:
Happy Accidents #6

Colourful, playful, happy.
Exploring blocks of color & a dash of perspective. 

üÑ∑üÑ∞-6 incorporates 9 palettes (out ot 18) from community members:
Woot, Margarine, Baiwei, Mac, DoktorKrabba, Prime, Bullseye, Nicholas & Guibo
